# Institutional design (BlackOut)

Read `blackout-web/DESIGN_BENCHMARK.md` before changing UI.

**Bar:** Bloomberg density · TradingView quote clarity · Stripe trust · Linear restraint.

**Never:** military copy, ◆ sigils by default, scanlines, text-glow on prices, fake LIVE badges, Anton titles in-app, emoji padlocks in nav.

**Always:** `FreshnessChip` for live state, JetBrains Mono for numbers, Syne/Inter for tool titles, plain professional copy.
